Text.string: Kill everyone for the Twin Gods!
You are in for a world of hurt!
I'm gonna kill everything I see!
Better not get in my way!
Ohp. A little poop came out!
This isn't even my final fart!
I'll split you in two! MAYBE THREE!
Come kill the Vault Thieves, or I'll kill you myself!
I'm gonna disembowel you for that!
That's MY TIME in there! MY TIME!
Get that crap away from me!
MY RAGE HAS SERVED A HIGHER PURPOSE!
THE TWINS WILL BRING ME BACK!
I WILL ALWAYS CHERISH THE TIME WE HAD TOGETHER!
I AM REAL! NOW I'M COMIN' FOR YOU, JEREMY!
DEATH IS NOT THE FINAL GATE!
You'll have to do better than th-- [death howl]
FINALLY I'M DEAD ON THE OUTSIDE TOO!
JOKES ON YOU! I WAS IN MASSIVE DEBT!
Gonna crack your chest and turn you inside out!
I'll turn your organs into a fine mist!
Yes! Gonna choke the life outta ya!
I'm gonna bind my wounds with your gut!
I'll choke you with your own arms!
Rip off your foot and shove it up your own ass!
I'm gonna beat you to death with your own skull!
I want my pounds of flesh!
I'm gonna rip open every soft part you have!
Put your blood in a bucket and paint my house!
It's only torture if no one's watching!
Your skull's gonna make a good hand puppet!
I'm gonna make a toothbrush outta your bones!
I'm gonna hit you until I stop hitting you! Which is never!
Your tongue's gonna make a lovely necklace!
Your beating heart's gonna feel good in my fist!
I'm gonna eat your brain and spit out your memories!
Looks like brain's back on the menu!
Break your bones into splinters and shove them into your ears!
I'm gonna put your own damn fist down your throat!
I was always too much for you!
You thought you could stand up to me?!
You stay right there, you dead prick!
Killing makes me feel so alive!
Wake up and let me beat you some more!
Gonna roast you like a pig!
You'd better not get back up!
Fee fie screw you, I'm gonna kill you! I'M GONNA KILL YOU!
You can't get away from me!
Come back here and face your death!
I'm gonna rip your throat out when I find you!
Come back here and get your skull cracked!
Just give me something to crush!
This is how you know I'm serious!
Come here and give me a hug!
Gonna crush your head between my hands!
You like what I've done with my hair?!
What's wrong? Don't you think I'm pretty?!
Feels so good to be out of that helmet!
I'll pop you like a zit!
